Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.06,0:02:19.76,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,250)\blur4}瞬間撰寫出意料之外的傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.98,0:02:22.45,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,250)\blur4}瞄準目標1！2！3！
